The below details explain how the module will be used , installed and its purpose in the accounting module 

PURPOSE
 For businesses which provide utilities to their clients eg. power , water and gas  need to track their client's consumption so that they can charge them . The below custom module can be used to provide businesses a more accurate way of billing their clients 

 *
 *
 *

PROBLEM SOLVED 
 The below module automates the manual billing process of consumable resources thus this hastens business operations

 *
 *

INSTALLATION
 The below module is developed with the odoo 17 version. 
  First uncompress the module
  Copy the module to the custom addons directory you may have created or have to create
  In the odoo interface activate developer mode , then update your app list.
  Search for the module then click activate to install it.

*
*

DEPENDENCIES
 You should have the invoicing module installed in your odoo instance
 

 
